Raymann Rayy(born 11 October) is an Indian actor, director and record label owner. He is a founder and owner of Raymann Rayy Productions. Aafreen sung by Ash King is the first song under his Production, composed by Agnel Roman and published by Nikhil Paul George (NPG Music). He is known for his work as an actor and director in Aafreen published by Nikhil Paul George.
